rComments: Knows in and out about finance and economics. Excellent lectures, not to forget his typical jokes. Best Prof in MBA.
Excellent professor.  By far the best in the Ottawa U program.
Professor Rahman is extremely knowledgeable, cares about his students and is passionate about economics.  He is a very dynamic teacher.

An interesting funny lecturer who clearly knows his stuff and manages the class expertly (so that the loudmouths don't take over).  Economics can be boring but he makes the material highly entertaining (profits?  who needs profits?)
The best Prof in the whole MBA program
One of the best professors ever. Truly amazing guy!
Professor Rahman focuses on the big picture and he has the ability to explain concepts in a very clear and thought out manner.  The best professor in the School of Management!
He is the BEST prof for corporate finance and economics and pretty much anything he teaches

Wonderful professor. Inspires and rewards learning. Has won MBA teaching reward 3 years running --no mystery as to why. This professor is brilliant -has pride and professionalism when teaching -treats class with repect and is inspired to ensure your personal success as a student of his teaching.
